1
00:01:03,690 --> 00:01:05,910
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:09,690
[Episode 15]

3
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,400
Li,

4
00:01:15,870 --> 00:01:17,640
what's so great about him?

5
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,570
Just because he's the Emperor?

6
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:25,120
Why don't you see me?

7
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,020
Can't you feel

8
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,590
my true feelings?

9
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,920
I have nothing but

10
00:01:33,229 --> 00:01:34,590
hatred for you.

11
00:01:37,830 --> 00:01:39,030
It seems...

12
00:01:40,090 --> 00:01:41,810
you've truly forgotten.

13
00:01:45,300 --> 00:01:46,310
Please, sir, I beg you.

14
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,229
I'm begging you.

15
00:01:47,229 --> 00:01:48,070
Get lost!

16
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:50,289
Skinny as a twig—

17
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:52,060
not fit to be a guard
in General Xun's mansion!

18
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:53,450
I can do anything.

19
00:01:53,509 --> 00:01:54,280
My father is sick.

20
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,590
I desperately need money.

21
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:56,120
Get lost!

22
00:02:00,390 --> 00:02:01,160
General.

23
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,080
He's already told you that you're not fit.

24
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,400
Why don't you listen?

25
00:02:10,430 --> 00:02:12,470
General, I really...

26
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:16,560
I'll give you a chance

27
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,310
for your filial piety.

28
00:02:18,510 --> 00:02:21,240
Come and fight with me.

29
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,750
If you survive after
half an incense stick burns,

30
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:26,240
I'll take you in.

31
00:02:26,950 --> 00:02:29,160
General, I... I dare not.

32
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:32,410
If you don't dare, I'll break your legs

33
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:33,750
and send you begging.

34
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:34,430
Stop!

35
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,500
Sir,

36
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:47,170
what honor is there in bullying the weak?

37
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,240
Do you

38
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:53,240
want to be my guard too, miss?

39
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:55,240
I might consider it.

40
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,240
Is that so?

41
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,280
Sir,

42
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,590
it seems

43
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,040
I've won this round.

44
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,590
Go now.

45
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:29,560
I had never seen

46
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:32,870
a woman as reckless as you.

47
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,310
From that day on,

48
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:37,030
I asked around about your identity.

49
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,630
Li,

50
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,030
you're too special.

51
00:03:42,730 --> 00:03:43,820
So,

52
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:48,030
you can only be mine.

53
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:51,430
You just want to bully me

54
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:54,350
to save your own face.

55
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:57,520
You pathetic, insecure thing.

56
00:03:58,590 --> 00:04:01,280
Shut up! I said shut up!

57
00:04:16,829 --> 00:04:19,029
You're trying to provoke me to kill you?

58
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:21,950
Don't worry, I won't let you have it.

59
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:30,240
Li,

60
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,680
tell me,

61
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,920
how would Xie Jiuzhao feel

62
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,360
if he knew I had taken you

63
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:42,390
before he dies?

64
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,360
Finally here.

65
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:52,480
The show begins.

66
00:04:58,570 --> 00:04:59,790
[Chunliu Garden]

67
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,920
Zhao！

68
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,950
Run, Zhao!

69
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,270
Zhao, leave me!

70
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:41,390
Go now, Zhao!

71
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:01,390
Xie Jiuzhao,

72
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:04,920
come on, save your Li.

73
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:05,950
Zhao,

74
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:07,180
it's their trap.

75
00:06:07,210 --> 00:06:08,960
Go now, Zhao!

76
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:10,000
Attack!

77
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:28,680
Zhao.

78
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:50,310
Xie Jiuzhao,

79
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,390
weren't you so capable?

80
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:55,560
Why do you look like a defeated dog now?

81
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,720
Xun Simo,

82
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,720
if you've got the guts, come at me!

83
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,040
Let Jiang Li go!

84
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,920
Zhao.

85
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,920
Fine. Then get on your knees

86
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:05,630
and beg me.

87
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,070
Xun Simo!

88
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,060
Hurry up,

89
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:14,560
or I'll snap her neck.

90
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,430
-Zhao.
-Li.

91
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,920
Zhao.

92
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,920
You shouldn't have come here, Zhao.

93
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:43,510
You are my Li.

94
00:07:43,530 --> 00:07:44,460
Zhao.

95
00:07:44,490 --> 00:07:46,290
How could I leave you alone?

96
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:50,920
If we can't escape today,

97
00:07:51,730 --> 00:07:53,330
I'll be with you till the end.

98
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:01,810
You're seeking death!

99
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,590
Stay away!

100
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,230
Xie Jiuzhao,

101
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,760
you're not getting
out of here alive today!

102
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,610
Slut.

103
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:40,030
No!

104
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:50,550
I gave you a chance.

105
00:09:02,510 --> 00:09:03,240
Li.

106
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,750
I said

107
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:24,870
I would make you pay with your life

108
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,630
to avenge Xi'er.

109
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:32,750
Li,

110
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,840
when you strike,

111
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:38,720
make sure you see clearly.

112
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,040
I want you

113
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:44,000
to remember how I look when I die.

114
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:55,960
Don't be afraid.

115
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,270
It's over now. It's over.

116
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:30,150
Zhao. Zhao.

117
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:31,840
Zhao!

118
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,270
Zhao!

119
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:34,790
Zhao!

120
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,270
Zhao.
